3.10. If (a) $f(x)=x^{2}$ and (b) $f(x)=\left\{\begin{array}{ll}x^{2}, & x \neq 2 \\ 0, & x=2\end{array}\right.$, prove that $\lim _{x \rightarrow 2} f(x)=4$.

