$$
\frac{\tan ^{-1} b-\tan ^{-1} a}{b-a}=\frac{1}{1+\xi^{2}} \quad a<\xi<b
$$

Since $\xi>a, 1 /\left(1+\xi^{2}\right)<1 /\left(1+a^{2}\right)$. Since $\xi<b, 1 /\left(1+\xi^{2}\right)>1 /\left(1+b^{2}\right)$. Then

