& =\frac{\partial^{2} U}{\partial \rho^{2}}+\frac{1}{\rho} \frac{\partial U}{\partial \rho}+\frac{1}{\rho^{2}}+\frac{\partial^{2} U}{\partial \phi^{2}}+\frac{\partial^{2} U}{\partial z^{2}}
