\left.\int_{x=0}^{\infty} \frac{e^{\alpha x} \cos r x}{-x}\right|_{\alpha=a} ^{b} d x=\int_{\alpha=a}^{b} \frac{\alpha}{\alpha^{2}+r^{2}} d \alpha
$$

i.e.,

