& =2^{2 p-1} B\left(p+\frac{1}{2}, P+\frac{1}{2}\right)=\frac{2^{2 p-1}\left\{\Gamma\left(p+\frac{1}{2}\right)\right\}^{2}}{\Gamma(2 p+1)}
\end{aligned}
$$

Then, since $I=J$,

